    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()


            <p>
                THIS IS A TEST!! <br />
                Hip & Clavicle is an Etsy shop that sells handmade jewelry and accessories. The business is owned and operated by a designer named Jillian,
                who creates unique pieces inspired by her love of vintage and bohemian style. Hip & Clavicle's product line includes necklaces, earrings,
                bracelets, and rings, all made with high-quality materials such as gold-filled and sterling silver wire, semi-precious gemstones, and freshwater
                pearls. Many of the pieces feature delicate and intricate wire wrapping and weaving techniques, giving them a one-of-a-kind, artisanal look. In addition
                to their handmade jewelry, Hip & Clavicle also offers a selection of hair accessories, including hairpins and combs adorned with pearls and crystals.
